Requirements:

- php >= 5
- mySQL >= 4.1
- php-mysql
- imagemagick
- ffmpeg
- flvtool2

For installation read INSTALL

Source Style:

- Valid php 5 code
- Class names have the first letter capitalized
- Private functions have a prefix of an underscore ("_")
- Indent of 2 spaces, no tabs (php and html output)
- Indents are in BSD/Allman style. See
  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indent_style
- Documentation style of doxygen

Patches:

- Send patches from the currenct subversion repository to patch@phtagr.org.

Commits:

- Add dash and filename at commit comments (e.g. "- File.php: Fixed")
